summary: When you really want to hear the whole album live, meaning acoustic dwoht & sig, but still want a throwback surprise song and...
body: When you really want to hear the whole album live, meaning acoustic dwoht & sig, but still want a throwback surprise song and can’t stop wondering what it could be and then you’re like ok I could hear THE SONG that made me feel all the feelings and decide then and the there that I NEEDED to know all of taylor’s music BUT this might be the only chance to hear every song on rep BUT it also might be the only chance to hear THE SONG and then the other songs that had THAT IMPACT each album and it’s like how do you pick????
